languages.text: "А похоже, что мне есть что терять? По-моему, ты мне одолжение собираешься оказать. Так что это, милосердие или месть?"
"Does it look like I have anything to lose? The way I see it, you are doing me a favour here. So which one is it: mercy or revenge?"

languages.text: « Vous avez l'impression que j'ai quelque chose à perdre ? Je crois plutôt que vous allez me rendre un service. Alors, qu'est-ce que ce sera : miséricorde ou vengeance ? »
languages.original_text: "Does it look like I have anything to lose? The way I see it, you are doing me a favour here. So which one is it: mercy or revenge?"

traits.locale_text: « Vous avez l'impression que j'ai quelque chose à perdre ? Je crois plutôt que vous allez me rendre un service. Alors, votre réponse : miséricorde ou vengeance ? »

languages.text: «¿Tengo pinta de tener algo que perder? Desde mi perspectiva, me está haciendo un favor. Bueno, dígame: ¿es por clemencia o por venganza?».
languages.original_text: "Does it look like I have anything to lose? The way I see it, you are doing me a favour here. So which one is it: mercy or revenge?"

traits.locale_text: «¿Tengo pinta de tener algo que perder? Para mí que me está haciendo un favor. Bueno, dígame: ¿clemencia o venganza?».

languages.text: “你觉得，我还有什么舍不得的东西吗？在我看来，你送我上路是在帮我的忙。所以，到底是什么呢？是仁慈，还是报复？”
languages.original_text: "Does it look like I have anything to lose? The way I see it, you are doing me a favour here. So which one is it: mercy or revenge?"

traits.locale_text: “你觉得，我还有什么舍不得的东西吗？我觉得你送我上路是在帮我的忙。所以，到底是什么呢？是仁慈，还是报复？”

languages.text: 「私に失うものがあるように見えるか？私からしてみれば、あんたは私に好意を持っているようだ。さて、これは慈悲か復讐、どっちだ？」
languages.original_text: "Does it look like I have anything to lose? The way I see it, you are doing me a favour here. So which one is it: mercy or revenge?"

traits.locale_text: 「私に失うものがあるように見えるか？私からしてみれば、あんたは私に好意を持っているようだ。さて、これは慈悲か復讐、どっちだ？」

languages.text: "Sieht es aus, als hätte ich irgendwas zu verlieren? So wie ich das sehe, tut Ihr mir hier einen Gefallen. Also, was darf es sein: Gnade oder Rache?"
languages.original_text: "Does it look like I have anything to lose? The way I see it, you are doing me a favour here. So which one is it: mercy or revenge?"

traits.locale_text: "Sieht es aus, als hätte ich irgendwas zu verlieren? Ich glaube, Ihr tut mir hier einen Gefallen. Also, was darf es sein: Gnade oder Rache?"

languages.text: "Kaybedecek bir şeyim varmış gibi mi duruyor? Bence bana iyilik ediyorsunuz. Soruma cevap ver: Merhamet mi yoksa intikam mı?"
languages.original_text: "Does it look like I have anything to lose? The way I see it, you are doing me a favour here. So which one is it: mercy or revenge?"
